==Finnish==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|fi|fiu-fin-pro|*armo}} (compare {{cog|et|arm}}, {{cog|izh|armo}}, {{cog|liv|arm}}, {{cog|vot|armo}}), derived from {{der|fi|gem-pro|*armaz||poor, pitiful, pitiable}} (whence {{m|fiu-fin-pro|*armas}} > {{m|fi|armas}}).

===Pronunciation===
{{fi-p}}

===Noun===
{{fi-noun}}

# [[grace]]
# [[mercy]]
#: ''Peli on suunniteltu lauantaiksi, mutta olemme vielä sään '''armoilla'''.''
#:: The ball game is scheduled for Saturday, but we're still at the '''mercy''' of the weather.

